# <%= it.displayName %>

<%= it.description %>

Generated by [MCP Tool Generator](https://github.com/example/mcp-tool-generator) using `mcp==1.27.1` (FastMCP).

## Quick start

```bash
uv sync
cp .env.example .env
uv run server.py
```

For manual testing via stdin/stdout:

```bash
echo '{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"method":"tools/list","params":{}}' | uv run server.py
```

## Connecting to Claude Desktop

Add to `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "<%= it.serverName %>": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": ["--directory", "/absolute/path/to/<%= it.serverName %>", "run", "server.py"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Connecting to Claude Code

```bash
claude mcp add <%= it.serverName %> -- uv --directory /absolute/path/to/<%= it.serverName %> run server.py
```

## Connecting to Cursor

Add to `~/.cursor/mcp.json` (global) or `.cursor/mcp.json` (project-local):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "<%= it.serverName %>": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": ["--directory", "/absolute/path/to/<%= it.serverName %>", "run", "server.py"]
    }
  }
}
```

