## Development

```bash
uv run pytest          # run tests
uv run ruff check .    # lint
uv run ruff format .   # format
```

## Security note

This server uses the MCP stdio transport. The host process (Claude Desktop, Claude Code, Cursor) manages the server lifecycle. No network port is exposed.

---

This project was generated with production standards applied — see [STANDARDS.md](STANDARDS.md) for what was applied and why.

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `LOG_LEVEL` | `info` | Logging verbosity. One of `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error`. |
| `RATE_LIMIT_MAX` | `100` | N/A — stdio transport has no HTTP layer. |
